    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices used in weaving, comprising a comb-like bar with evenly spaced pins along the long side, used to space the warp threads.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
